header.header
  .container
    .header-inner
      .header-inner__logo Dreamshare
      .header-inner__log
        .header-inner__log__item
          a(href='#') Log in
        .header-inner__log__item.active
          a(href='#') Sign up
.top-page
  .intro
    .container
      .intro-inner
        .intro-inner__title Share your holiday dream
        .intro-inner__suptitle And find the perfect partner to fullfill it
        button.intro-inner__button(type='button') Find your holiday partner
main
  .container
    section.section
      h2.section-name How Dreamshare works?
      .d-flex.justify-content-between.row
        .col-xl-4.col-lg-4.col-md-4.col-sm-4.col.col-12
          .section-item-1
            img(src='../images/Step_1.png' alt='')
            .section-item-1__wrap
              .section-item-1__wrap_step Step 1
              .section-item-1__wrap_subheading Sed leo enim, condimentum
              .section-item-1__wrap_text
                | Quisque libero libero, dictum non turpis in, luctus
                | semper lorem. Donec rhoncus a leo sit amet facilisis.
        .col-xl-4.col-lg-4.col-md-4.col-sm-4.col.col-12
          .section-item-1
            img(src='../images/Step_2.png' alt='')
            .section-item-1__wrap
              .section-item-1__wrap_step Step 2
              .section-item-1__wrap_subheading Morbi velit risus
              .section-item-1__wrap_text
                | Nulla venenatis tempor dui in molestie. Nulla quis
                | dictum purus, sit amet porttitor est.
        .col-xl-4.col-lg-4.col-md-4.col-sm-4.col.col-12
          .section-item-1
            img(src='../images/Step_3.png' alt='')
            .section-item-1__wrap
              .section-item-1__wrap_step Step 3
              .section-item-1__wrap_subheading Sed leo enim, condimentum
              .section-item-1__wrap_text
                | Quisque libero libero, dictum non turpis in, luctus
                | semper lorem. Donec rhoncus a leo sit amet facilisis.
    section.section
      .section-name Meet a partner for your best holiday
      .d-flex.justify-content-between
        .row
          .section-item-2.col-xl-3.col-lg-3.col-md-6.col-sm-6.col.col-12
            img.section-item-2__avatar(src='../images/Avatar_1.png' alt='')
            .section-item-2__name Bradley Hunter
            .section-item-2__home
              | Based in Chicago. I love playing tennis and loud music.
          .section-item-2.col-xl-3.col-lg-3.col-md-6.col-sm-6.col.col-12
            img.section-item-2__avatar(src='../images/Avatar_2.png' alt='')
            .section-item-2__name Marie Bennett
            .section-item-2__home
              | Currently living in Colorado. Lover of art, languages and
              | travelling.
          .section-item-2.col-xl-3.col-lg-3.col-md-6.col-sm-6.col.col-12
            img.section-item-2__avatar(src='../images/Avatar_3.png' alt='')
            .section-item-2__name Diana Wells
            .section-item-2__home
              | Living in Athens, Greece. I love black and white classics,
              | chillout music and green tea.
          .section-item-2.col-xl-3.col-lg-3.col-md-6.col-sm-6.col.col-12
            img.section-item-2__avatar(src='../images/Avatar_4.png' alt='')
            .section-item-2__name Christopher Pierce
            .section-item-2__home
              | Star Wars fanatic. I have a persistent enthusiasm to
              | create new things.
      .section-button
        button.section-button_2(type='button') See other partners
    section.section
      .section-name Discover holiday activity ideas
      .section-gallery.row
        .section-gallery__img.img-small.col-xl-4.col-lg-4.col-md-4.col-sm-12.col.col-12
          img(src='../images/Sport.png' alt='')
          .section-gallery__img_inscription Sports and Activities
        .section-gallery__img.img-small.col-xl-4.col-lg-4.col-md-4.col-sm-12.col.col-12
          img(src='../images/Health.png' alt='')
          .section-gallery__img_inscription Wellness and Health
        .section-gallery__img.img-small.col-xl-4.col-lg-4.col-md-4.col-sm-12.col.col-12
          img(src='../images/Extreme.png' alt='')
          .section-gallery__img_inscription
            | Extreme Sports
            | and Expeditions
        .section-gallery__img.img-small.col-xl-4.col-lg-4.col-md-4.col-sm-12.col.col-12
          img(src='../images/Games.png' alt='')
          .section-gallery__img_inscription Games
        .section-gallery__img.img-big.col-xl-8.col-lg-8.col-md-8.col-sm-12.col.col-12
          img(src='../images/Culture.png' alt='')
          .section-gallery__img_inscription Culture and Education
        .section-gallery__img.img-big.col-xl-8.col-lg-8.col-md-8.col-sm-12.col.col-12
          img(src='../images/Relax.png' alt='')
          .section-gallery__img_inscription Enjoyment and Relaxation
        .section-gallery__img.img-small.col-xl-4.col-lg-4.col-md-4.col-sm-12.col.col-12
          img(src='../images/Travel.png' alt='')
          .section-gallery__img_inscription Travelling
    section.section
      .section-name Create your holiday activity
      div
        .section-inscription Hi! What are your holiday interests?
        .section-activity
          input.section-activity__input(type='text' minlength='6' placeholder='Enter your insterests')
          button.section-activity__button(type='button') Search partners
